---
title: Open-Faced Mushroom and Chicken Breast Melts with Balsamic Onions and Potato Wedges
description: Crisp ciabatta rolls topped with hearty mushrooms, jammy balsamic onions and chicken are a match made in sandwich heaven. Melted mozzarella is the bonus you never knew you wanted, but absolutely need!
